              "id": "32695c61",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"51\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"51\">Upholstery &amp; Leather Care for Commercial Spaces</strong></h2><p data-start=\"53\" data-end=\"300\">From reception seating to executive chairs, your facility\u2019s upholstered and leather furnishings are part of your brand. Over time they collect dust, oils, spills, and wear, which affects the impression you make on clients, visitors, and employees.</p><p data-start=\"302\" data-end=\"494\">At Midland Floor Care, we run a complete, professional cleaning process that restores fabric and leather surfaces to a fresh, reliable state, extends their life, and keeps your space inviting.</p><p data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"545\"><strong data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"545\">Why businesses need upholstery &amp; leather care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"546\" data-end=\"847\"><li data-start=\"546\" data-end=\"626\"><p data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"626\">Preserve brand standards: clean, well kept furnishings project professionalism</p></li><li data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"696\"><p data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"696\">Extend furniture life: prevent fiber breakdown and leather cracking</p></li><li data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"768\"><p data-start=\"699\" data-end=\"768\">Improve indoor air quality: remove allergens, dust, and trapped odors</p></li><li data-start=\"769\" data-end=\"847\"><p data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"847\">Protect high traffic assets: maintain the look and feel of investment pieces</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"894\"><strong data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"894\">Our upholstery &amp; leather cleaning process</strong></p><ul data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"1338\"><li data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"992\"><p data-start=\"897\" data-end=\"992\">Assessment and fabric testing: identify material type and condition to choose the safest method</p></li><li data-start=\"993\" data-end=\"1065\"><p data-start=\"995\" data-end=\"1065\">Pre treatment: gentle commercial grade solutions loosen embedded soils</p></li><li data-start=\"1066\" data-end=\"1150\"><p data-start=\"1068\" data-end=\"1150\">Deep extraction or hand cleaning: targeted processes for fabric, vinyl, or leather</p></li><li data-start=\"1151\" data-end=\"1262\"><p data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1262\">Conditioning and protection: specialized moisturizers and sealants for leather to prevent drying and cracking</p></li><li data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1338\"><p data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1338\">Final inspection: every detail checked to meet our Midland Shine Standard</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1340\" data-end=\"1369\"><strong data-start=\"1340\" data-end=\"1369\">Ideal commercial settings</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1516\"><li data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1406\"><p data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1406\">Corporate offices and boardrooms</p></li><li data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1440\"><p data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1440\">Hotel lobbies and guest areas</p></li><li data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1469\"><p data-start=\"1443\" data-end=\"1469\">Healthcare waiting rooms</p></li><li data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1497\"><p data-start=\"1472\" data-end=\"1497\">Restaurants and lounges</p></li><li data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"1516\"><p data-start=\"1500\" data-end=\"1516\">Retail showrooms</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1518\" data-end=\"1551\"><strong data-start=\"1518\" data-end=\"1551\">Why choose Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1780\"><li data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1625\"><p data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1625\">Expertise across fabric types, stitching styles, and leather finishes</p></li><li data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1684\"><p data-start=\"1628\" data-end=\"1684\">Tailored methods that balance safety and effectiveness</p></li><li data-start=\"1685\" data-end=\"1746\"><p data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1746\">Flexible scheduling: nights, weekends, and off peak hours</p></li><li data-start=\"1747\" data-end=\"1780\"><p data-start=\"1749\" data-end=\"1780\">Guaranteed results on every job</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1782\" data-end=\"1847\">Your furnishings are more than seats. They\u2019re part of your brand.</p><p data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1939\">Let Midland Floor Care\u2019s upholstery and leather cleaning help them stand the test of time.</p><p data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"1969\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you,<br data-start=\"1951\" data-end=\"1954\" />Justin Campbell</p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your On-Site Visit!</a>\u00a0<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/staff-training/\">Staff Training</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/eco-friendly-floor-solutions-for-retail-stores/\">Eco-Friendly Floor Solutions for Retail Stores</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/jobs/\">Jobs</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li>\n</ul>",
